{"tid":1956735,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"與病毒撞名的墨西哥啤酒Corona宣布配合抗疫而停產","createTime":"2020-04-03T11:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T15:38:34.000Z","uid":28114,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"659c0b1ba338a51d04a5cbbc25aaaab6206a2bf5","tid":1956735,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/0403_corona-990x520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F0403_corona-990x520.jpg&h=7f2fa4c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情一發不可收拾，至今全球確診人數破100萬。墨西哥一個叫Corona的啤酒品牌因與病毒名稱「Cornonavirus」相似，突然惹起關注。墨西哥政府日前下令暫停所有「非必要活動」至4月底，Corona酒廠也隨即宣布配合措施停產。<br />\n<br />\nCorona啤酒隸屬墨西哥最大釀酒廠Grupo Modelo，集團旗下還有Pacifico以及Modelo。集團發聲明表示正減低產量，並於周日起停產。<br />\n<br />\n由農業及糧食生產不用停產，集團期望當局澄清啤酒是否需要停產，若果政府批准，他們可以讓75%員工在家工作，並確保啤酒供應。<br />\n<br />\nCorona啤酒「不幸」與冠狀病毒英文撞名，美國一間公關公司早前訪問700多人，有38%受訪者指現時在任何情況下都不會購買Corona啤酒，16%人質疑啤酒是否與病毒有關，14%的Corona啤酒常客也表示不會在公眾場合買該牌子的啤酒。甚至曾有網絡謠言指，Corona啤酒的銷量在疫情爆發後在美國急降4成，品牌的美國代理商就否認傳聞，更指Corona啤酒於2月升5%。<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥至今有1510人確診武漢肺炎，有50人死亡，目前已宣布全國進入緊急狀態，停止一切非必要活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/489022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F489022&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bq7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=1f1a16a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/489022</a>"},{"pid":"36a1863a2c31fef82618ab50008916103ce217b2","tid":1956735,"uid":143598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac335d0a51ddecb316c09de00ac561f1fc76b6bf","tid":1956735,"uid":6103,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"reply